description:
  We derive formulas for the derivatives of general order for the functions
$z^{-
u}h_{
u}(z)$ and $z^{
u}h_{
u}(z)$, where $h_{
u}(z)$ is a Bessel,
Struve or Anger-Weber function. These formulas are motivated by the occurrence
of the expressions $ rac{d^n}{dz^n}(z^{-
u}I_{
u}(z))$ and
$ rac{d^n}{dz^n}(z^{-
u}K_{
u}(z))$ in the study of Variance-Gamma
approximations via Stein's method.
